Kylie,

Please help donate and use your platform to raise money and awareness for the terrible bushfires 🔥 happening in Australia.

Billions of animals have been lost in the fire especially the Koalas and Kangaroos who are native to Australia. 😭

Please come together and help us as any donations would be appreciated.

Global warming is real, we need to come together and help one another as its our planet and affects everyone living on it. Everyone needs to do their bit to try reduce temperatures rising any further.

If you love animals or have been to Australia and seen these beautiful creatures give what you can so our volunteers who are working so hard can help save them. Any donations big or small all count and if everyone in the world donated just $1 it would make a world of difference.

I will provide the links bellow and am trying to do my bit to bring awareness to the devastation occurring in our home land:


https://www.gofundme.com/f/help-save-kangaroo-islands-koalas-and-wildlife


https://www.gofundme.com/f/save-our-koala-bushfire-victims

https://www.gofundme.com/f/aj6zpu-port-stephens-koalas

https://www.gofundme.com/f/sa-koala-burn-victims

There are many other go fund me pages so please give what you can and lets spread to love to all affected areas. Hoping 🙏🏼 this will make a difference 💓❤️
